# Script 4: Communication Infrastructure
# Visualize cell towers, radio towers, TV towers, and coverage
# Shows signal strength heatmap across city
# Enables device localization via triangulation

# Load tower data from OSM
towers load
  cell towers (OpenCellID)
  radio towers
  tv transmission towers

# Visualize coverage
show signal strength heatmap
show tower locations as points
show coverage zones as contours

# Compute coverage metrics
coverage area within city
signal strength at random points
triangulation capability check

# Display results
towers report
coverage report
signal strength metrics
